# 21st.dev Components — Installation Plan

## Goal
Safely integrate 15 components from the `unleft.comp` staging project into the main UNLEFT website. Components will be migrated **one by one** upon user request to ensure clean implementation and proper styling alignment.

## Source & Staging
- **Source**: `c:\Work\unleft.space\unleft.comp\` (Next.js project with installed components)
- **Staging Area**: `src/components/21st/` (Contains pre-moved components and hooks for quick migration)
- **Hooks**: `src/hooks/` (Contains shared utilities like `use-debounced-dimensions.tsx`)

